 one second, which is an interesting observation to keep in mind for performance evaluations.\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "Implemented Pulsar client integration tests for `org.apache.pulsar:pulsar-client:4.2.1`.\n\nChanges made:\n- Replaced placeholder test with `PulsarClientTest`.\n- Added Testcontainers dependency:\n  - `tests/src/org.apache.pulsar/pulsar-client/4.2.1/build.gradle`\n- Added required Docker images file:\n  - `tests/src/org.apache.pulsar/pulsar-client/4.2.1/required-docker-images.txt`\n- Added tests covering:\n  - Standalone Pulsar broker startup via `apachepulsar/pulsar:4.2.1`\n  - Producer/consumer byte message flow with key, properties, acknowledgement, and `MessageId` roundtrip\n  - JSON schema producer and reader flow from earliest position\n  - String producer and shared consumer builder paths\n\nI did not compile, run, or verify the tests, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_035cf556d8082acd016a28fd1983488194b56c5b5e62fea062\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1037, "output": 1037, "cacheRead": 28672, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 30746, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1781071105537, "responseId": "resp_035cf556d8082acd016a28fd0200cc8194bd9bc8a409f22cae"}}
