"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Investigating message serialization**\\n\\nI’m thinking there could be a special marker involved that might cause an `UnsupportedOperation`. I'm curious about whether `MessageId` with `ledgerId -1` is something to consider for `earliest/latest`. The method `toByteArray` might serialize correctly, and `MessageId.fromByteArray` seems likely to produce an equal `MessageIdImpl`. There could be potential issues with creating `Schema.JSON(Order.class)` using Jackson, especially if Order metadata isn't generated correctly. I wonder if the user-code filter involves any tests. I'll look into that more closely.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_Rew1IVrhQ3pTfYpIKXTDaodD|fc_035cf556d8082acd016a28ff30b3508194a5397b517270e60b", "name": "read", "arguments": {"path": "tests/src/org.apache.pulsar/pulsar-client/4.2.1/user-code-filter.json"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 522, "output": 378, "cacheRead": 32256, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 33156, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1781071650944, "responseId": "resp_035cf556d8082acd016a28ff2590b48194added50a680c640b"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_Rew1IVrhQ3pTfYpIKXTDaodD|fc_035cf556d8082acd016a28ff30b3508194a5397b517270e60b", "toolName": "read", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "{\n  \"rules\": [\n    {\n      \"excludeClasses\": \"**\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"includeClasses\": \"com.scurrilous.circe.**\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"includeClasses\": \"org.apache.avro.reflect.**\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"includeClasses\": \"org.apache.pulsar.**\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1781071665017}]}
